{"tid":22880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"減肥成功嘅肥仔，你問我答！","createTime":"2016-12-04T16:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-04T17:51:04.000Z","uid":52703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd810df57f87b09d560860d03fc5de4b1af7f4dd","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"歷史：<br />\n以前四十三寸腰<br />\n高180<br />\n二百一十幾磅<br />\n依家：<br />\n三十四腰<br />\n高180<br />\n一百八十左右<br />\n<br />\nbmi唔可以做準，我有舉鐵<br />\n可以叫半肥瘦叉燒"},{"pid":"7df0e164696670d394d498accbc1555d5a8903d1","tid":22880,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"條J有無長返"},{"pid":"eed1f7c2450c6abbe039605197ae71ffa29f9e7b","tid":22880,"uid":37671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:02:34.000Z","msg":"伯母幾好嘛？"},{"pid":"6d19c2f9e99e6aa791678f21664b2056a232eded","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條J有無長返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有，不過仲有少少皮摺要時間收返"},{"pid":"84797008dc5ded75f3cd9360547ad5c868e998c1","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伯母幾好嘛？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身體一向都唔好，早幾年大手術，身體麻麻"},{"pid":"38679fedf35d244e5f8278548b3130c05789ea64","tid":22880,"uid":25384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"用咩方法減？"},{"pid":"06dc9acab738d9d2fa5d68df10c80db5c0066d8a","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用咩方法減？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n減肥冇捷徑，一定要做運動，我係跑步落磅"},{"pid":"568cc1dd8635c208d893d67f9fd42ea8c4ffe0dc","tid":22880,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>條J有無長返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有，不過仲有少少皮摺要時間收返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果收唔到皮打算點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ef9270f205cf270012fec29cb8a0a7d1bfa918","tid":22880,"uid":25384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用咩方法減？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n減肥冇捷徑，一定要做運動，我係跑步落磅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一星期幾次？<br />\n<br />\n再加舉鐵？"},{"pid":"7eeb197c0b0e700dbb2feb27a7e3d4971f7e7cac","tid":22880,"uid":13809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"一星期跑幾次？<br />\n每次跑幾耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bd1d40f8e54a936ec661d24c6496555356feae","tid":22880,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:10:28.000Z","msg":"一唔跑又升番, 一個月1kg, 屌"},{"pid":"88955441d87a76358a7ef020be6de2205986ab16","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條J有無長返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有，不過仲有少少皮摺要時間收返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果收唔到皮打算點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會收唔番，要時間嘅<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係體適能導師"},{"pid":"876afc704e0871b92128d27c53e76d4f14c8e5ae","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:11:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用咩方法減？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n減肥冇捷徑，一定要做運動，我係跑步落磅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一星期幾次？<br />\n<br />\n再加舉鐵？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一星期一次，有時行吓山，有時跑下步"},{"pid":"8e7bbbbf97df5360c29b087d3b048ae8fe2fa9b9","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一唔跑又升番, 一個月1kg, 屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會重返，不過控制響180左右"},{"pid":"435712448e5b4e9ab9f6f728305ae8c30847396b","tid":22880,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"可唔可以帶我減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1479cb8561baf16d633440d78e616c1cb003686","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以帶我減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我帶就難道高啲，俾個建議你可以係飲食着手<br />\n 我小學可以一餐食三個出前一丁， 一包廚師腸加<br />\n一個椰菜<br />\n中學一餐三個飯盒<br />\n<br />\n大專開始節制， 例如每晚食紅米， 雞肉同菜"},{"pid":"5d4068637c4909e2f6963851b29a940666362b56","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一星期跑幾次？<br />\n每次跑幾耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔日跑，每次跑3千米<br />\n<br />\n以前覺得好辛苦， 跑兩個籃球場都收皮<br />\n<br />\n依家可以叫跑得到， 雖然跑唔快<br />\n最遠試過屯門跑到元朗"},{"pid":"6aa4781ac572e891da4d9cebcd3a1f7edb6a15fd","tid":22880,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一唔跑又升番, 一個月1kg, 屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會重返，不過控制響180左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經177lbs, 年中先170lbs <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b60c5eec741724204902747c46e4d9ffce35fd","tid":22880,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:29:38.000Z","msg":"巴打高都好...又矮又肥真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跑係咪唔洗快..最緊要KEEP住<br />\n點樣知自己跑左3千米<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e9c73a2ad09a1b8b779a291900b38bbedab3d0","tid":22880,"uid":55541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:32:04.000Z","msg":"點對抗誘惑"},{"pid":"24fd7bbc4e15facd665fab352b8c73c0ccbd4177","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打高都好...又矮又肥真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跑係咪唔洗快..最緊要KEEP住<br />\n點樣知自己跑左3千米<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗快，最緊要你跑得到<br />\n如果你真係唔識嘅，可以用巴士站計數<br />\n<br />\n我以前係用學校有一條路線3千米， 後尾用輕鐵站計數，<br />\n跑距離算啦"},{"pid":"8d9c8607fd3e343de170056e2b1e0bec379ef101","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一唔跑又升番, 一個月1kg, 屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會重返，不過控制響180左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經177lbs, 年中先170lbs <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾好唔錯， 大家齊俾心機"},{"pid":"8b240072ecc16de7ef2031fd016107536c72ba2f","tid":22880,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:36:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"af7c200efca2e4b0927eca16f24ad9bd35400b84","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點對抗誘惑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食飯之前諗一諗，盡量唔食煎炒煮炸嘅物體"},{"pid":"70ab719e16bca03f283e04a9b0c67708eac6a5f8","tid":22880,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:38:16.000Z","msg":"咁重隻腳受唔到wow巴打"},{"pid":"487255d8f097cb613117832bf7e007fe360a851d","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"由於外表睇唔出，好多人都覺得我基本冇咁重，所以中央肥胖，瘦左之後好多人都唔認得"},{"pid":"f65f00b38af5ca8d050d7554414c30170fa73ee4","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁重隻腳受唔到wow巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有一段時間有少少痛，果斷時間轉左游水，後尾又跑返步<br />\n依家好正常乜事都冇，個人仲輕鬆左好多"},{"pid":"c8536dfa7df74513021b71b4cc2311bb559bd463","tid":22880,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於外表睇唔出，好多人都覺得我基本冇咁重，所以中央肥胖，瘦左之後好多人都唔認得</blockquote><br />\n台灣個小豬讀書時都係大肥仔<br />\n有個暑假減肥<br />\n之後返學D同學都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96988a0208bb13308c574fa8225f6b65dcc4464f","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由於外表睇唔出，好多人都覺得我基本冇咁重，所以中央肥胖，瘦左之後好多人都唔認得</blockquote><br />\n台灣個小豬讀書時都係大肥仔<br />\n有個暑假減肥<br />\n之後返學D同學都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得個樣好似冇乜分別，人哋話我下巴好尖<br />\n身型上仲有肚腩，不過細咗好多，我會努力少少，好快減埋"},{"pid":"aefcb3a196a5c032069a2a1a631c9ad67a6b5d2b","tid":22880,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"條j長左幾多"},{"pid":"870a7789829716c94514008f4d3d6df8c44621f9","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條j長左幾多</blockquote><br />\n目測1cm多啲，冇度過"},{"pid":"0a85ae3610aef554d036293b8db30779165432ab","tid":22880,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:04:11.000Z","msg":"肥矮毒留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係第一日減, 跑2下都喘氣<br />\n見到呢個po有返哂動力<br />\n<br />\n利申: 162, 73公斤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf0a6e6fde603d9d84227482cc0f7b21aa9597f","tid":22880,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"我都想跑步減肥 但左邊膝頭長期隱隱作痛<br />\n係咪唔適合跑步減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔跑步仲可以點減 定照可以慢跑<br />\n<br />\n利申接近二百磅 好彩夠高睇落唔算太肥"},{"pid":"9dc5fa2a3de9efba2cac38019639df9a96f9573f","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥矮毒留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係第一日減, 跑2下都喘氣<br />\n見到呢個po有返哂動力<br />\n<br />\n利申: 162, 73公斤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俾啲心機啦，一開波係覺得好悶， 減到肥其實好開心"},{"pid":"cbad56a70a34d6258887e27112ff15562ab152aa","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想跑步減肥 但左邊膝頭長期隱隱作痛<br />\n係咪唔適合跑步減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔跑步仲可以點減 定照可以慢跑<br />\n<br />\n利申接近二百磅 好彩夠高睇落唔算太肥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多啲游水，得閑拉下筋，唔好做一啲跑步嘅動作，好返先至做， 拉筋係一個好緊要嘅動作，可能你本身重，游水應該比較適合你"},{"pid":"8e1c5c3e61ef7ac1636f542dcad1ccd206a13035","tid":22880,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以帶我減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我帶就難道高啲，俾個建議你可以係飲食着手<br />\n 我小學可以一餐食三個出前一丁， 一包廚師腸加<br />\n一個椰菜<br />\n中學一餐三個飯盒<br />\n<br />\n大專開始節制， 例如每晚食紅米， 雞肉同菜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你宜加日日三餐食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c751032da76aaa62ec5f4b6d990e19766932457","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以帶我減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我帶就難道高啲，俾個建議你可以係飲食着手<br />\n 我小學可以一餐食三個出前一丁， 一包廚師腸加<br />\n一個椰菜<br />\n中學一餐三個飯盒<br />\n<br />\n大專開始節制， 例如每晚食紅米， 雞肉同菜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你宜加日日三餐食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早餐乜都得，午餐乜都得，晚飯好節制<br />\n都係果句盡量唔好食咁肥，好輕鬆"},{"pid":"49e4757e1c96b2a1b96365bdd63afaec1b618f8f","tid":22880,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:57:05.000Z","msg":"想問每日跑三千米做sit up,掌上壓個d夠唔夠?<br />\n同埋平時會唔會出街食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想咁快有糖尿病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:175cm 87kg 但係睇落似七十幾kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"