replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:55:56.000Z","msg":"180高 164磅 有踢開波 隻腳有肌肉<br />\n想減肥好耐 個肚下半部同個肥仔波都有啲大 <br />\n<br />\n始終都戒唔到食&hellip;&hellip;我都知一定要均衡飲食同做有氧運動 但有心冇力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e14e547d80da9ed6d266fed102ea1c7d6b273d","tid":22880,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>180高 164磅 有踢開波 隻腳有肌肉<br />\n想減肥好耐 個肚下半部同個肥仔波都有啲大 <br />\n<br />\n始終都戒唔到食&hellip;&hellip;我都知一定要均衡飲食同做有氧運動 但有心冇力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇好似話要做啲重量運動 我其實係想一路減一路操肌 平時跑完步自己係公園做啲力量訓練有冇用"},{"pid":"b0ae6567bb57d8a0e96499de677a09e947f4e978","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>180高 164磅 有踢開波 隻腳有肌肉<br />\n想減肥好耐 個肚下半部同個肥仔波都有啲大 <br />\n<br />\n始終都戒唔到食&hellip;&hellip;我都知一定要均衡飲食同做有氧運動 但有心冇力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇好似話要做啲重量運動 我其實係想一路減一路操肌 平時跑完步自己係公園做啲力量訓練有冇用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放心，亂咁做好快冇心機"},{"pid":"644e0c869b93b454190bf8003a3c4c1e371872df","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"跑步真係好見效，可以長遠跑，落磅好快"},{"pid":"131cdb8de40f6d20baa30d42ec0f8e84026ed382","tid":22880,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:58:00.000Z","msg":"今日係第三日返工前跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跑20分鐘到就無氣，之後又行下跑下咁，總共用左35分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪無乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：高181-183，今朝磅187磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b1619e74a14b9832a31595c33e96fa557a9bc5","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日係第三日返工前跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跑20分鐘到就無氣，之後又行下跑下咁，總共用左35分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪無乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：高181-183，今朝磅187磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前都係咁，不過長遠D跑我已經好似冇乜感覺，師兄俾啲心機， 我建議睇一個時間盡量跑， 唔好停，唔好行"},{"pid":"7e891a0698b2c592ba945442ddb2fa24684c16cd","tid":22880,"uid":17598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:33:28.000Z","msg":"跑步跑街定跑步機?<br />\n我次次跑完第日磅重都會重左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知搞乜"},{"pid":"5ea254ff865ab0f00df3fc3bfd0a515b5c037910","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑步跑街定跑步機?<br />\n我次次跑完第日磅重都會重左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" cla