8a1da6fc31f99baf2ee44b5456732df03f9e","tid":22880,"uid":29127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"減左肥個身型會唔會似女人"},{"pid":"426bfe2c0a148259f67dda09d4ff8872ce92c882","tid":22880,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:43:56.000Z","msg":"圖呢？"},{"pid":"a7b3ebd3d80852270637b1de292c8291b6b73c11","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減左肥個身型會唔會似女人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥仔波要時間減，不過我練上胸所以唔似，柱狀咁"},{"pid":"cd02cfa51073ffb55a97a8cce69024b08c1fab8a","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLjOcM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLjOcM2.jpg&h=876ec9b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1592984d2aaa7f09dfaa2d4a7daa9dce1f617f20","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有真相"},{"pid":"e01b903761868a78c49cc8fad6382a05867efabf","tid":22880,"uid":15206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLjOcM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLjOcM2.jpg&h=876ec9b7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似都仲有少少肥仔波"},{"pid":"0f799d7d10ff8e5cbd3d3d78d05d5f491726519c","tid":22880,"uid":2093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:47:00.000Z","msg":"你隻腳有冇瘦左？<br />\n我減左半年，肚腩收左好多，但大小腿仲係好粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a1b9340c6a0fc72317f52eaf903e4cefc4fb08","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你隻腳有冇瘦左？<br />\n我減左半年，肚腩收左好多，但大小腿仲係好粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我隻腳瘦先，可能你做運動時間唔夠長，下下爆炸力，隻腳仲未收落嚟"},{"pid":"dbdaf98cffba1fdf99e5fd4ecba2949b553a7822","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLjOcM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLjOcM2.jpg&h=876ec9b7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似都仲有少少肥仔波</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁當然啦，時間問題"},{"pid":"b37a91052438f9a1b716e4c42aa2f80811b97c4b","tid":22880,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一星期跑幾次？<br />\n每次跑幾耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔日跑，每次跑3千米<br />\n<br />\n以前覺得好辛苦， 跑兩個籃球場都收皮<br />\n<br />\n依家可以叫跑得到， 雖然跑唔快<br />\n最遠試過屯門跑到元朗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跑 跑步機得唔得? 最好跑幾耐 重磅"},{"pid":"1d72edc4de703a9499cdffe46555324a01b0097f","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一星期跑幾次？<br />\n每次跑幾耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔日跑，每次跑3千米<br />\n<br />\n以前覺得好辛苦， 跑兩個籃球場都收皮<br />\n<br />\n依家可以叫跑得到， 雖然跑唔快<br />\n最遠試過屯門跑到元朗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跑 跑步機得唔得? 最好跑幾耐 重磅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多教練都會主張你跑跑步機，跑步機係可以嘅，但係你要記得一樣野， 跑到冇乜進步空間你就要出街跑，有好多人都習慣咗響健身室做倉鼠，30分鐘以上你先可以做到帶氧運動，覺得痛或者唔舒服，就要休息"},{"pid":"d7256244d6ca2bd678dbd75bba4fa9b80c43e28e","tid":22880,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:16:08.000Z","msg":"我180cm<br />\n<br />\n80kg<br />\n<br />\n有個肥仔波想減<br />\n<br />\n我要直接去舉鐵定係帶氧好？<br />\n<br />\n體脂23%<br />\n<br />\n求樓主指點下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69d674d4ca82d5fa356ec6b055a14c391aeeb49","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:20:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我180cm<br />\n<br />\n80kg<br />\n<br />\n有個肥仔波想減<br />\n<br />\n我要直接去舉鐵定係帶氧好？<br />\n<br />\n體脂23%<br />\n<br />\n求樓主指點下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶氧，我同你差唔多，我會選擇跑步"},{"pid":"c2f7dc69bc54039db87880a09d66225675a1374d","tid":22880,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我180cm<br />\n<br />\n80kg<br />\n<br />\n有個肥仔波想減<br />\n<br />\n我要直接去舉鐵定係帶氧好？<br />\n<br />\n體脂23%<br />\n<br />\n求樓主指點下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶氧，我同你差唔多，我會選擇跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跑步一星期跑幾多次？<br />\n每次跑幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c683cacaa20ae2781dcb31a371144557f27ffe9","tid":22880,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一星期跑幾次？<br />\n每次跑幾耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔日跑，每次跑3千米<br />\n<br />\n以前覺得好辛苦， 跑兩個籃球場都收皮<br />\n<br />\n依家可以叫跑得到， 雖然跑唔快<br />\n最遠試過屯門跑到元朗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跑 跑步機得唔得? 最好跑幾耐 重磅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多教練都會主張你跑跑步機，跑步機係可以嘅，但係你要記得一樣野， 跑到冇乜進步空間你就要出街跑，有好多人都習慣咗響健身室做倉鼠，30分鐘以上你先可以做到帶氧運動，覺得痛或者唔舒服，就要休息</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解會無乜進步空間 肥仔唔想係街比人望住跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127f2225f0b068b33d6347a38200ca698a62137d","tid":22880,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:30:42.000Z","msg":"減肥減左九個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n78變65kg<br />\n<br />\n靠隔日舉鐵同跑步<br />\n<br />\n戒甜野同宵夜最緊要<br />\n<br />\n依加懶左三日先跑步同舉鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n照戒甜野<br />\n<br />\n依加keep 住起65唔上唔落<br />\n<br />\n但仲有小腩同微波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2add312f642655269491d1124f3bcb2ec70e6cd3","tid":22880,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"其實去健身室 冬天跑有冇效果 我試過 2日跑一次跑左一星期都無效 同埋好難出汗"},{"pid":"3a023f7e8ea5f544f24229aecb456827c2a85d30","tid":22880,"uid":2093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你隻腳有冇瘦左？<br />\n我減左半年，肚腩收左好多，但大小腿仲係好粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我隻腳瘦先，可能你做運動時間唔夠長，下下爆炸力，隻腳仲未收落嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前120kg太重 ，所以淨係玩太空漫步同踩單車，每次30-40分鐘"},{"pid":"1180493b53d13d7178b37cb104e6505613e6154f","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我180cm<br />\n<br />\n80kg<br />\n<br />\n有個肥仔波想減<br />\n<br />\n我要直接去舉鐵定係帶氧好？<br />\n<br />\n體脂23%<br />\n<br />\n求樓主指點下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶氧，我同你差唔多，我會選擇跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跑步一星期跑幾多次？<br />\n每次跑幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一星期三四日可以嘅話，幾耐睇情況，不過一定over半個鐘以上"},{"pid":"3c20641e4452407e6634c770fc4b447ee6edae59","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你隻腳有冇瘦左？<br />\n我減左半年，肚腩收左好多，但大小腿仲係好粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我隻腳瘦先，可能你做運動時間唔夠長，下下爆炸力，隻腳仲未收落嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前120kg太重 ，所以淨係玩太空漫步同踩單車，每次30-40分鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以去下一啲有溫水池嘅泳池游， 重點係注意返飲食調節"},{"pid":"8bc96fffd0b843ab05bacb8f9834db1818d6bb89","tid":22880,"uid":1874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"180 180bls<br />\n都仲係肥仔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：185 187bls減左2,3個月去到165bls 之後依家又肥返去187bls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85196dd62f71244c26e61031e2407bf0f07f8a02","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減肥減左九個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n78變65kg<br />\n<br />\n靠隔日舉鐵同跑步<br />\n<br />\n戒甜野同宵夜最緊要<br />\n<br />\n依加懶左三日先跑步同舉鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n照戒甜野<br />\n<br />\n依加keep 住起65唔上唔落<br />\n<br />\n但仲有小腩同微波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家都一齊俾心機，好快減到肥"},{"pid":"db5a1cf3e7aba14e153757bc7f895c281bc147be","tid":22880,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9516035e419bc0132cff4f87518ea372ae601e16","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跑 跑步機得唔得? 最好跑幾耐 重磅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多教練都會主張你跑跑步機，跑步機係可以嘅，但係你要記得