"89196b093ae0054db40aa49670bdbce7a9d687f8","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難解釋你聽，總之係健身室跑點樣都冇喺街跑有成效</blockquote><br />\n真係唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋你跑果陣，肚</blockquote><br />\n腩會唔會痕?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解會痕？"},{"pid":"a23dd321c6732eef704d88ce8e676ae145ef1fd0","tid":22880,"uid":23364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以帶我減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我帶就難道高啲，俾個建議你可以係飲食着手<br />\n 我小學可以一餐食三個出前一丁， 一包廚師腸加<br />\n一個椰菜<br />\n中學一餐三個飯盒<br />\n<br />\n大專開始節制， 例如每晚食紅米， 雞肉同菜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解同你食既野一樣 又係紅米雞菜 <br />\n<br />\n我肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d199e39b2baa93fb9f56d189652ea2c64a51cac3","tid":22880,"uid":5702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以帶我減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我帶就難道高啲，俾個建議你可以係飲食着手<br />\n 我小學可以一餐食三個出前一丁， 一包廚師腸加<br />\n一個椰菜<br />\n中學一餐三個飯盒<br />\n<br />\n大專開始節制， 例如每晚食紅米， 雞肉同菜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解同你食既野一樣 又係紅米雞菜 <br />\n<br />\n我肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食三碗同半碗都好大分別既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df4dfb0f99d7731750e0e39228f863fead56c2d","tid":22880,"uid":65612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難解釋你聽，總之係健身室跑點樣都冇喺街跑有成效</blockquote><br />\n真係唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋你跑果陣，肚</blockquote><br />\n腩會唔會痕?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解會痕？</blockquote><br />\n有時可能磨擦到痕，同埋肚右手邊會痛"},{"pid":"e936fe26a1ced7f0dfddeac7486ffb3aa233e736","tid":22880,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n腩會唔會痕?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解會痕？</blockquote><br />\n有時可能磨擦到痕，同埋肚右手邊會痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁應該係你個人問題姐"}]}